WEBVTT

00:02:27.280 --> 00:02:30.401
are the seeds of real learning,

00:02:30.401 --> 00:02:32.515
not some scripted curriculum

00:02:32.515 --> 00:02:35.811
that gave them tidbits of random information.

00:02:35.811 --> 00:02:39.283
In May of 2010, at 35 years old,

00:02:39.283 --> 00:02:42.376
with a two-year-old at home and my second child on the way,

00:02:42.376 --> 00:02:44.992
I was diagnosed with a large aneurysm

00:02:44.992 --> 00:02:47.512
at the base of my thoracic aorta.

00:02:47.512 --> 00:02:50.564
This led to open-heart surgery. This is the actual real email

00:02:50.564 --> 00:02:52.098
from my doctor right there.

00:02:52.098 --> 00:02:55.623
Now, when I got this, I was -- press Caps Lock --

00:02:55.623 --> 00:02:58.088
absolutely freaked out, okay?

